<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Survey</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; line-height:1.5;">

    <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <h1 style="color: #333333; text-align: center;">Considering a 0 to 10 scale, how likely would you recommend our company to a friend? </h1>
                <p style="color: #666666; text-align: center;">It's easy to answer, just click on a rate below!</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0;">
                <table align="center" border="2" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=0&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">0</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=1&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">1</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=2&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">2</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=3&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">3</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=4&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">4</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=5&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">5</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: red;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=6&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">6</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: goldenrod;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=7&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">7</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: goldenrod;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=8&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">8</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: forestgreen;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=9&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">9</a>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: forestgreen;">
                            <a href="<%= @base_url %>/answer-nps?ticket=<%= @ticket %>&rate=10&hash=<%= @hash %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: white; font-weight: bold;">10</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="color: #666666;">Thank You!</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>
</html>
